satellite.heading: Saatalaayitii
satellite.specs:
Safartuu: 50x58x64 mm
1P KiishaaQube
Ulfaatina: 245 gr
Meeshaalee: aluminiyeemii, warqee, faayibargilaasii fi qaamolee elektirooniksii.
Orbiiti: Olka’iinsa 525 ± 25 km; garagalchuu: SSO 97.6 ± 0.1°
Launcher: PSLV (Polar Satellite Launch Vehicle) kan ISROn hojjetamu

antenna.heading: Anteenaa/Siidaa
antenna.specs:
Safartuu: 6 m (daayameetira) e 1.2m (olka'iinsa) .
Ulfaatina: 46 kg
Meeshaalee: aluminiyeemii, boordii daawwitii epooksii, golee aluminiyeemii warqee caasaa iskaafooldii keessaa fannifame.
